How can I pay tuition fees?.answer: You can pay tuition fees in several ways // Use QR CODE – the payment can be made online and is accepted until 23.00 น. // Pay in cash at the counters of Bangkok Bank, Krungthai, Kasikorn, Siam Commercial or Government Savings Bank – the cash window runs from 25 ถึง 29 April 2565 and follows the banks’ normal working hours. // Use a credit‑card at the university’s treasury office – the cut‑off time is 16.30 น. // Use an online credit‑card payment – it is accepted until 23.00 น. // If you have previously signed an agreement for automatic debit with Siam Commercial Bank, the fee can be deducted directly from your account, provided the account has sufficient balance and the service fee is covered. // Note that once a debit transaction has been processed, the system will not allow a duplicate automatic deduction.
